.value.resource_description: Congratulations! You've got a free textbook. Download this guide to learn how to use it.
Adapted from OpenStax College Success, this guide discusses effective reading approaches, study tips, and notetaking strategies for students.
Adapted from OpenStax College Success, this guide includes information about estimating time on tasks, avoiding procrastination, and using strategies to stick to your priorities.

.value.resource_heading: Instructional Videos, Concept Trailers, and Problem Solution Videos
.value.resource_description:
Access the videos of the AP® Physics Collection, organized in playlists by chapter on the OpenStax YouTube channel. 

Instructional videos feature AP® teachers and Rice professors teaching core material; Concept Trailers are Hollywood studio-produced videos that bring key physics concepts to life; and problem solution videos feature instructors walking through example problems from the text.
Click here to access our lab manual containing 20+ lab activities to guide students understanding of AP® concepts.
